1
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,680
Thank you, Master Konghui,

2
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:39,520
for bringing Lin Feng's armor

3
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,960
from the Divine Machine Battalion's altar.

4
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,000
I cannot repay this great kindness.

5
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,280
If Linggu Temple ever needs Blossom Pavilion's help,

6
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,640
I,

7
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,720
will do my utmost.

8
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,840
It was merely a small effort.

9
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:57,320
For my Linggu Temple to exist peacefully in this world,

10
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:00,240
it must stand outside the Three Realms.

11
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:02,840
No need to be polite.

12
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:06,760
Here are the Divine Machine Battalion's

13
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,480
three hundred soldiers' Eight Characters of Birth.

14
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,000
I ask you, Master,

15
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:12,320
to set up memorial tablets for them in Linggu Temple

16
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,000
and perform deliverance for their grievances.

17
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:16,400
I wish to donate all the pension money from this merit

18
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,240
to Linggu Temple.

19
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,480
Worldly possessions...

20
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,960
you should take them back.

21
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,360
If left here,

22
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:38,120
they would only be enjoyed by the greedy.

23
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,360
How about this,

24
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,360
play a game of chess with me.

25
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,040
Alright.

26
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,600
Wait.

27
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,960
Let's play Gomoku.

28
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,800
Master, your chess skills are superb.

29
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,400
Why are you obsessed with Gomoku?

30
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,960
You see, throughout my life,

31
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,360
I have traveled far and wide.

32
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,360
My chess skills...

33
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,200
are unsurpassed by anyone.

34
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,880
But now,

35
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,520
confined in this mountain temple,

36
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,080
watching the mundane world with a cold eye...

37
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,120
Only you,

38
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,400
and playing with my closed-door disciple Tang Xi,

39
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:29,200
brings true freedom and joy.

40
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:31,720
Good.

41
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:32,800
Then let's play Gomoku.

42
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,040
Next,

43
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:52,680
taking down Shang Hua will be even harder.

44
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:57,720
You...

45
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:05,120
you can't hold your liquor.

46
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,280
Look at you...

47
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,200
how will you ever find a wife?

48
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:14,200
He risks his life for this cause;

49
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,960
how could he think of settling down?

50
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,240
I've worked so hard,

51
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,440
shouldn't you praise me?

52
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,720
Now that we've stepped on the tiger's tail,

53
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,040
if we don't kill the tiger,

54
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,160
we are the ones who will die.

55
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,280
Actually,

56
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,600
the key to taking down Shang Hua lies with Wang Zhi.

57
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,440
Wang Zhi is the Western Depot Eunuch Lord groomed by Shang Hua.

58
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:47,040
All the things the Eastern Depot did,

59
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,280
all the shady business,

60
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,440
Wang Zhi was involved in.

61
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,920
That Zhang Yi...

62
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,680
if not for Shuoyue's sake back then,

63
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,360
would he be alive today?

64
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,080
Three years of painstaking effort,

65
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,320
just for fear she would remember Lin Feng.

66
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,040
But unexpectedly,

67
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,440
the bugs remind her every day not to forget.

68
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,760
I told you long ago,

69
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,040
contact with bugs

70
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,240
will lead you astray.

71
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,760
Lin Feng was one,

72
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,360
Zhang Yi, Tang Xi...

73
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,600
if they hadn't provoked you,

74
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,920
I wouldn't be this tired.

75
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,200
Don't you dare

76
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,360
play the "kind father, filial son" act in front of me.

77
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,960
It's just checks and balances.

78
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,560
You're afraid I'll reveal the material I have,

79
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,080
expose it,

80
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,720
and implicate the Eastern Depot.

81
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,000
Today,

82
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,760
you brought him here to be taught,

83
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,400
but you forgot,

84
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:57,680
he is today what I was yesterday,

85
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:01,080
and will be tomorrow what I am today.

86
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:14,720
Youzhi is more humble and obedient than you.

87
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,480
I am very satisfied.

88
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,640
Shuoyue.

89
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,480
Shuoyue.

90
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,160
By the way.

91
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:04,760
I recognize you.

92
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,200
But you don't remember me.

93
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,560
You're so thick-skinned.

94
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,560
To treat your savior...

95
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,040
...by offering yourself in marriage?

96
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,320
That's repaying kindness with enmity.

97
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,640
There are many ways to repay a life-saving grace.

98
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,520
What's wrong?

99
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:22,960
They...

100
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,560
What is it?

101
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,840
There's a story there.

102
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
...has always had...

103
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,560
...inextricable ties with the Eastern Depot.

104
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,440
By using the Eastern Depot's secret intelligence...

105
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,520
...we can get the Western Depot abolished.

106
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:34,520
So...

107
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,280
...if we want to bring down the Eastern Depot...

108
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,600
...we must get the crucial intelligence held by the Western Depot.

109
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,200
This is what we must do next.

110
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,320
Right.

111
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,560
Everything you say is right.

112
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,600
You've been right since three years ago.

113
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,720
I'm the one who was always wrong.

114
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,160
What a...

115
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,440
...brilliant strategist...

116
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:05,440
...calculating Zhang Yi.

117
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,880
You make me look...

118
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,680
...just like a...

119
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,880
...joke.

120
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,480
Instead of talking nonsense here...

121
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,960
...we should be thinking about...

122
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:33,600
...picking a nickname for the unborn child.

123
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:35,880
I actually...

124
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:37,480
...have a good name ready.

125
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,120
I originally planned to save it for...

126
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,680
...my and Shuoyue's first child.

127
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,200
Who would have thought...

128
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:44,280
...you kid would beat me to it.

129
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,280
General, please.

130
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,960
In the unseen world...

131
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,240
...it is all destiny.

132
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,200
Tianguan.

133
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,640
As in "Heavenly Official Bestows Blessings".

134
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,040
But isn't the name Tianguan...

135
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,120
...a bit too grand?

136
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,760
Not at all.

137
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,560
When naming a child...

138
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,520
...you have to aim high.

139
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:09,920
A family of prosperity...

140
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:12,040
...deserves the blessing of the Heavenly Official.

141
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:12,760
As for me...

142
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:13,800
...I don't have anything precious...

143
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,320
...to gift to my brother.

144
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,160
This is Master Konghui's...

145
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,480
...incense-blessed peace coin.

146
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,200
It can bless the child with a smooth birth...

147
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,240
...and keep mother and child safe.

148
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,920
Such thoughtfulness...

149
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,480
...paired with my nickname...

150
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,200
...is a good omen, Shijie.

151
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:25,920
Good.

152
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,360
Then on behalf of the child...

153
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,040
...I accept these great gifts from his two godfathers.

154
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:45,800
General.

155
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,120
Shijie.

156
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,240
You're here.

157
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:58,960
Zhang Yi.

158
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,240
Listen to my explanation, Zhang Yi.

159
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,200
I did not defect to Wang Zhi of the Western Depot.

160
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,000
The plan to lure the enemy in deep...

161
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,360
...was truly intended for the battle.

162
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,080
It wasn't that I craved glory, Zhang Yi.

163
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:08,600
Zhang Yi!

164
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,000
Zhang Yi, listen to my explanation, Zhang Yi!

165
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,760
Zhang Yi, listen to me, Zhang Yi!

166
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,920
Don't go, Zhang Yi!

167
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:27,920
My lady.

168
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:29,800
Why are you here?

169
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:31,040
Where is Zhang Yi?

170
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,520
Where is General Lin?

171
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,440
Where is the Divine Machine Battalion?

172
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,560
Husband.

173
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,360
What's wrong?

174
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,880
This is our home in the capital.

175
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,800
There is no Divine Machine Battalion here.

176
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,600
That was all three years ago.

177
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,520
Why can't you let it go?

178
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,280
Let it go?

179
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,240
How can I let it go?

180
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,560
General Lin is gone.

181
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,240
The Divine Machine Battalion is gone.

182
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,240
Because of my proposal, they are all gone.

183
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,560
How do you expect me to let it go?

184
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,640
The General is gone.

185
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,120
The Divine Machine Battalion is gone.

186
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,040
Daddy, wake up, quick.

187
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:27,840
Daddy.

188
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,120
Daddy.

189
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,560
Daddy.

190
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:31,760
Daddy.

191
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,840
Tianguan'er.

192
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,960
Why is your breath so smelly?

193
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,160
If you don't wake up soon,

194
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,000
watch out, or Mom won't cook for us.

195
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:47,520
Your mother always has a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

196
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,320
What is that delicious smell?

197
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,240
The porridge Mom made.

198
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,280
Mom.

199
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,080
Mom.

200
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,120
Daddy isn't dead.

201
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,200
Daddy's awake.

202
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,640
Look, use your strength.

203
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:08,600
Right.

204
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:10,640
Right.

205
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,160
Swing it.

206
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,040
Like this.

207
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,360
Come on.

208
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,160
Slash again.

209
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:14,880
Slash.

210
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,320
Right.

211
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:18,920
Is this right?

212
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,000
Look.

213
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:25,480
Zhang Yi has always known what he wants.

214
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,160
Zhang Yi.

215
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,400
I will accompany you to send off the General.

216
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:30,960
Get away from me.

217
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,440
The General doesn't need a coward like you.

218
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,120
Get lost!

219
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,560
Until this vengeance is exacted,

220
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,040
I will not rest until I die.

221
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,240
Brother Lu.

222
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,200
I'm sorry.

223
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,200
You are different from me.

224
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,200
For the sake of your wife and child,

225
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,960
please live a good life.

226
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,080
Even if you have to crawl,

227
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,120
or kneel,

228
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:56,400
protect the happiness you have now,

229
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,760
at any cost.

230
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,120
For my sake,

231
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,560
for General Lin,

232
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:03,720
and the three hundred martyrs of the Divine Machine Battalion.

233
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,960
His heart held the whole world.

234
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:10,800
How could there be no grassland for a little wild foal?

235
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,880
Put your strength here.

236
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,280
Who goes there?

237
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,200
Can't you see Vice Minister Zhang of the Dali Temple

238
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,160
is passing through?

239
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:22,800
I am

240
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,720
Legal Advocate Lu Shijie of Shuntian Prefecture.

241
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,320
I pay my respects to Lord Zhang.

242
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,240
Lord Zhang.

243
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,600
You see, I didn't go to the Western Depot.

244
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,240
Instead, I went to Shuntian Prefecture to be a Legal Advocate.

245
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,560
I came here today

246
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,040
because I hoped that we brothers

247
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:36,920
could have a good talk.

248
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:56,880
Advocate Lu.

249
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,640
Have you misunderstood something?

250
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:00,920
Where you hold office,

251
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,160
or which big tree you rely on,

252
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:03,040
what does that have to do with me?

253
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,800
Even if you are at Shuntian Prefecture,

254
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,400
using your sharp tongue in the courtroom,

255
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,440
whether you are seeking justice for the people,

256
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,000
or colluding with officials to oppress them,

257
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:11,880
it has nothing to do with me.

258
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,480
A mere Legal Advocate

259
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,520
wanting to cling to the Vice Minister of the Dali Temple?

260
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:17,880
You're overestimating yourself.

261
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,680
So you are the Military Strategist who doomed

262
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,960
the three hundred soldiers of the Divine Machine Battalion.

263
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:27,000
What brilliant schemes you have, Strategist.

264
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,000
Next time, you'd best steer clear of the Dali Temple.

265
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:36,600
Just wait a little longer.

266
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:37,640
We're going home.

267
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,320
None of us has given up.

268
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,960
When the dust settles,

269
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,480
we will call each other brothers again.

270
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:54,920
Come.

271
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,080
Right. One more.

272
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,160
Why?

273
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,760
Why didn't you tell me the whole truth?

274
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,680
You really gathered a group of like-minded people,

275
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,640
brought them together,

276
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,440
and deceived everyone's eyes.

277
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:17,720
If in this world,

278
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,680
anger could sever bonds of friendship,

279
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,600
then they wouldn't be considered important people,

280
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,520
and there wouldn't be,

281
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,200
any story to follow.

282
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,480
If I couldn't even fool you,

283
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:34,760
how could I fool everyone else?

284
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,000
Besides, you are not alone.

285
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:38,520
There is also Tianguan'er,

286
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,480
and your sister-in-law to care for.

287
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:40,720
How could I put you,

288
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,720
in a dangerous position?

289
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,240
How do you know I couldn't help you?

290
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:45,800
Is it just because,

291
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,880
I am a useless scholar?

292
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,280
Do you know that for the past three years,

293
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:54,880
because of that proposal back then,

294
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:55,360
and my weakness,

295
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,120
do you know what torment I've endured?

296
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:01,080
I know you've suffered.

297
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,560
It is precisely because I know,

298
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:04,600
no matter how much you bear,

299
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:05,440
you will endure it,

300
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:06,760
that I entrusted the task,

301
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,240
of defending Tang Xi to you.

302
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,680
This matter isn't easy.

303
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,560
You simply don't know.

304
00:16:12,560 --> 00:16:13,560
You're just like those people,

305
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,360
you never believed in me from the start.

306
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:20,240
Actually, I know too.

307
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:21,920
If it weren't for me,

308
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,320
proposing the plan to lure the enemy in deep,

309
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:25,440
General Lin and the 300 Divine Machine Battalion troops,

310
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,840
wouldn't have fallen into Wang Zhi's trap,

311
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,240
and they wouldn't have lost their lives in vain.

312
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:28,840
Stop talking.

313
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:32,920
No matter what,

314
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:36,160
General Lin and the brothers aren't coming back.

315
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:40,640
Enough.

316
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,720
You have the temper of a cat,

317
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:44,960
yet you insist on acting like a tiger.

318
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,160
Vent your anger if you must,

319
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,280
but do you really intend to disown this brother?

320
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:50,920
Shut up.

321
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:54,520
Do you know that for these three years,

322
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,240
except for close family,

323
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:58,000
and those seeking profit,

324
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:01,120
I have suffered the world's disdain.

325
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,440
It seems all the vulgar words in this world,

326
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,480
were created for me alone.

327
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,320
Do you know that?

328
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,040
But it doesn't matter.

329
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:12,640
I can endure all these rumors and slander.

330
00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:15,080
But I hope,

331
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:18,360
but I hope my confidant, my brother,

332
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,440
could understand my resolve,

333
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,360
instead of being like the others,

334
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,120
viewing me as an incompetent coward afraid of death,

335
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,360
and keeping me out of it.

336
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,440
Truly,

337
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,160
a stubborn mule with a one-track mind.

338
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,640
Do you remember when I first sought you out for this cause?

339
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,000
You asked me, with so many legal advocates in the world,

340
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,320
why I chose you specifically.

341
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,320
What did I tell you?

342
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,040
You said,

343
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:58,480
you firmly believed,

344
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:02,040
that you and I are like-minded people.

345
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:03,520
You wanted me to strive,

346
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:05,040
to live with my head held high.

347
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,800
But before that,

348
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:11,240
you asked me to crush all my dignity,

349
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,400
on my knees.

350
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:32,880
Who do you think,

351
00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:34,920
told me all of this?

352
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,480
Plan phase two:

353
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,880
When you are captured and interrogated at the Dali Temple,

354
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:51,280
you must find and arrange a reliable legal advocate,

355
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,600
to defend you and get you out of the Dali Temple.

356
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,840
Herein I recommend the capital's Shuntian Prefecture's,

357
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,840
number one legal advocate, Lu Shijie.

358
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,880
The Tang Sect can investigate his background.

359
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,440
Though his nature is soft,

360
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:05,360
his value lies in how he cherishes loyalty and righteousness.

361
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:07,000
The world may bully him,

362
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:07,640
humiliate him,

363
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:08,400
slander him,

364
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:09,080
loathe him,

365
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:09,840
despise him,

366
00:19:10,360 --> 00:19:11,520
yet he can smile naively through it all,

367
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:13,200
never losing his original heart.

368
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:21,200
Where is he?

369
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:24,640
Tianguan'er.

370
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,240
I've tried so hard

371
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,880
Shouldn't someone praise me?

372
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,640
All these years

373
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,640
You've had it hard

374
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:08,960
Second Brother

375
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:09,720
Third Brother

376
00:20:14,360 --> 00:20:15,280
Are you crazy?

377
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:17,400
Wife

378
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:19,120
Come here, come here, come here

379
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:21,640
This is my Third Brother, Zhang Yi

380
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,760
Although he looks lazy and unrestrained

381
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:24,840
He is kind-hearted

382
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:25,440
Thoughtful

383
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:26,320
And his blade skills are superb

384
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,360
Tianguan'er, quick

385
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,480
Call him Third Father

386
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:30,400
Your son Lu Li greets Third Father

387
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:31,560
Little rascal

388
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:32,640
You're behaving now

389
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:34,360
I wondered what it was

390
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:36,560
I thought you were having another episode of hysteria

391
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,080
Second Brother has a hidden ailment

392
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:39,360
It's nothing

393
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,280
It's nothing

394
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,160
Inner demon

395
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:42,920
Since returning from the battlefield

396
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,920
He hasn't been able to move past it

397
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,840
He often wakes up at night

398
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:47,960
And runs out like a madman

399
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,360
He can't stand seeing red objects

400
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:59,400
It's a cliché trope

401
00:21:00,120 --> 00:21:01,760
A gentleman dies for a confidant;

402
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,760
sword in hand, he leaves the capital.

403
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,520
This is a man's romance

404
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,680
Since it's romantic

405
00:21:10,120 --> 00:21:12,080
How can it lack a beauty like me?

406
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,880
Then let's go home and eat

407
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:17,040
Let's go

408
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:25,520
Beauty's red sleeves, dew stains the sleeves

409
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:30,040
When flying flowers intoxicate, fragrance fills the city

410
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:35,320
Like auspicious signs falling from the heavens

411
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:41,280
Truly a fine sight in the human world

412
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:50,720
Weird old man

413
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,120
What are you thinking about?

414
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,240
Crazy girl

415
00:21:58,760 --> 00:21:59,160
Come

416
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:01,680
Let's go home

417
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:07,200
Go home and soak our feet

418
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:12,280
Are you here to verify an answer?

419
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:14,840
What answer?

420
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,160
The true flavor of life is simple joy

421
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:21,520
What we want has always been simple

422
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:24,000
For us, "ordinary"

423
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,960
Is the most unattainable thing

424
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,400
I'm here to find a cat

425
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:32,480
Let's go home

426
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,040
This lantern

427
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:51,040
Why is it different from the ones I usually see?

428
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:55,560
Things that pass through my hands

429
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,640
Are naturally different

430
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,480
An ordinary Sky lantern

431
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:01,920
The oil is lit

432
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:04,040
After burning inside the lantern for a while

433
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,480
It expands

434
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:06,880
Then you let go

435
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:08,560
And it flies up into the sky

436
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:10,840
But this one of ours

437
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:13,080
Is a Sky lantern for Consort Wan to see

438
00:23:13,600 --> 00:23:16,080
Naturally, we must use something special

439
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:17,160
Come

440
00:23:22,320 --> 00:23:22,880
Hold it well

441
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:42,800
Tianguan'er

442
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:44,960
Don't disturb your Uncle Wu.

443
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:46,760
Go back with your father.

444
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,640
A fair and gentle lady

445
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,440
is a fine match for a gentleman.

446
00:23:58,560 --> 00:23:59,680
How is the situation in the court?

447
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:02,560
No matter how Li Chenyang proves his innocence,

448
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:04,080
he can never become a second Yu Qian.

449
00:24:04,560 --> 00:24:05,360
In the court,

450
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:07,520
his accumulated merits have long aroused jealousy.

451
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,240
No one pleads for him anymore.

452
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,320
And His Majesty certainly won't admit to the world

453
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,640
the unjust cases mishandled by the Western Depot.

454
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:17,520
That Lord Li can be pardoned and return home

455
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:19,960
is enough for him to live out his days in peace.

456
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:21,840
The Eastern Depot

457
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,280
neither suppressed nor pleaded for Wang Zhi.

458
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:26,520
They responded to changes by remaining unchanged.

459
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,520
At a time like this, Shang Hua

460
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:30,440
would absolutely not stick his neck out.

461
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:32,080
The new Minister of War

462
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:34,080
was originally set to be a crony of the Eastern Depot.

463
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,040
But after this incident,

464
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:39,240
it was changed to an old official of the court.

465
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:41,440
Although he is also mediocre and slick,

466
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,960
he never favors any one power faction.

467
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,880
Years of scheming for military power

468
00:24:47,560 --> 00:24:48,840
have all come to nothing in the end.

469
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:53,560
Come on.

470
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:01,640
I'll block one of yours.

471
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,320
Are you sure?

472
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:44,640
Five in a row.

473
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:45,480
I win.

474
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,080
Has anyone ever said

475
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,480
playing chess is not as good as watching it?

476
00:25:53,520 --> 00:25:55,080
The observer has no stake in winning or losing,

477
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,760
so they can truly enjoy the fun of the game.

478
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:00,840
Whose brilliant idea is that?

479
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:03,040
My father.

480
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:04,560
It seems Minister Yuan

481
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:06,080
has been guiding Battalion Commander Yuan well lately.

482
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:08,840
Lord Zhang,

483
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:11,240
didn't you use to

484
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,720
act all high and mighty, unwilling

485
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:13,520
to stay here a moment longer?

486
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:16,880
Why are you making eyes at her now?

487
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:18,880
What did you two do while I was away?

488
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:19,880
Shoo, shoo.

489
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,080
Battalion Commander Yuan,

490
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:26,280
you missed out on several thousand taels of gold,

491
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:28,280
plus your first awakening of love.

492
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,560
What are you all hiding from me?

493
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:34,200
A man's intuition tells me

494
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:35,200
it's definitely not simple.

495
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,920
A "little adult" is still

496
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,480
a hundred thousand miles away from being a man.

497
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:42,240
Since you're so sincere,

498
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,640
do you want to consider

499
00:26:44,600 --> 00:26:45,600
taking me as your master?

500
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,600
See no evil,

501
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:51,960
hear no evil.

502
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:57,480
The Imperial Decree arrives!

503
00:27:07,360 --> 00:27:08,880
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Zhang Yi, receive the decree!

504
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,120
By the will of the Heavens,

505
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,680
the Emperor decrees:

506
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:17,360
Regarding the abduction case of Li Chenyang,

507
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,400
the Dali Temple has performed with merit.

508
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,640
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Zhang Yi,

509
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:25,440
captured the treasonous rebels hiding in Linggu Temple.

510
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:28,160
He is specially awarded one thousand taels of gold,

511
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:31,240
two strings of Master Konghui's agarwood prayer beads,

512
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:32,840
and a set of Feiyu Robe.

513
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:34,440
This is to commend his loyalty and integrity.

514
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,440
Respect this.

515
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,440
Long live the Emperor, long live, long long live.

516
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:44,600
Everyone who comes is a guest.

517
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:46,520
If you don't mind,

518
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:47,680
on ordinary days, you can also

519
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,840
come sit in my small courtyard.

520
00:27:49,320 --> 00:27:49,880
After all,

521
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:52,880
I am just an idler who pretends to be refined.

522
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:56,120
Young Master Tang is indeed generous.

523
00:27:56,520 --> 00:27:58,640
It's just that your vision is a bit short-sighted.

524
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,080
But then again,

525
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:01,640
here at your place,

526
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,520
you are indeed no vulgar man.

527
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:07,960
I have important matters to handle at the Eastern Depot.

528
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:09,280
Lord Zhang,

529
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:10,400
I take my leave.

530
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,240
Farewell, Lord Song.

531
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:25,360
It seems Lord Shen still has business with me.

532
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,560
Consort Wan...

533
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:30,680
to mourn the passing of Master Konghui,

534
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:33,560
plans to, on the seventh day of his passing,

535
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,040
hold a Prayer Lantern Festival.

536
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:36,920
This is the invitation.

537
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,080
A Prayer Lantern Festival?

538
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:43,560
Will all the court officials attend?

539
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,040
Naturally, officials of the fourth rank and above.

540
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:48,360
Today,

541
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:51,440
Lord Song and I went to the Dali Temple to find you.

542
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,040
But Danqing said

543
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:54,880
you had come here.

544
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,400
I didn't believe it at first.

545
00:28:57,520 --> 00:28:59,560
I didn't expect to witness such a scene with my own eyes.

546
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,720
Although the closing statement paints a different picture,

547
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:04,240
but the truth within...

548
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:06,880
don't you know it, Lord Zhang?

549
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:09,160
Since when did Lord Zhang

550
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,320
become just like Battalion Commander Yuan,

551
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,360
so rash and frivolous?

552
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:15,560
I originally thought

553
00:29:15,840 --> 00:29:17,520
Lord Shen was merely bound hand and foot

554
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,680
by dogma and etiquette.

555
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,440
I never imagined

556
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:22,360
that your soul was never free either.

557
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,640
They associate with me;

558
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,120
how does that make them rash and frivolous?

559
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:28,280
Young Master Tang's skill with glib words has grown.

560
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:28,880
Not convinced?

561
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:30,800
If not, let's go outside and fight!

562
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:31,840
All right, all right.

563
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:33,520
What are you two bickering about?

564
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:34,960
Lord Shen,

565
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,640
you can't out-talk her or out-fight her.

566
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:37,560
It's pointless.

567
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,200
Let's disperse.

568
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:51,680
Battalion Commander Yuan,

569
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:53,920
since you've managed to leave the Minister's manor,

570
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:55,840
the Imperial Guard has plenty of matters to handle.

571
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:58,000
There's no time for you to idle here.

572
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,600
Come with me, now.

573
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,480
What are you shouting for?

574
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:04,440
Did you eat gunpowder?

575
00:30:08,360 --> 00:30:09,040
What is it?

576
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:14,480
If you don't want to bring trouble to the Minister's manor lately,

577
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:16,440
you'd best not hang around Tang Xi and Zhang Yi.

578
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,760
Tang Xi is just that kind of jianghu woman;

579
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:19,480
I can understand that.

580
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:21,200
But Lord Zhang is our colleague.

581
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,240
How is that forming a clique?

582
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,080
External thieves are easy to fight;

583
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,120
internal thieves are hard to guard against.

584
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,000
Time and again, they step on the tiger's tail,

585
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,360
trying to beat it to death and skin it,

586
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:29,440
provoking the tiger to strike back with vicious force.

587
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,640
If a vicious tiger harms the people of a region,

588
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,560
doesn't it deserve to die?

589
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:43,120
This Imperial Court...

590
00:30:44,040 --> 00:30:46,200
really gives rewards in real gold and silver.

591
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,760
I even got this Feiyu Robe.

592
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:52,560
But then comes Consort Wan's Prayer Lantern Festival.

593
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:55,240
Seeing how Shen Youzhi can't hide his thoughts,

594
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:57,480
I fear he has guessed something.

595
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:01,120
If it's a blessing, it's not a curse;

596
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:02,760
if it's a curse, it cannot be avoided.

597
00:31:06,840 --> 00:31:09,720
Doesn't this give you the perfect opportunity?

598
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:12,600
Opportunity?

599
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:16,920
You mean Consort Wan's Prayer Lantern Festival?

600
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,960
For us to enter the Western Depot's secret intelligence agency

601
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:19,840
is very simple.

602
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:21,880
That place...

603
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,200
I could lead you in with my eyes closed.

604
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:27,520
But to get the incriminating records of the Eastern Depot,

605
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:30,680
one must possess the nine-linked ring key.

606
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:33,200
So, have you found out the key's whereabouts?

607
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:36,080
Recently, my people in the palace found out

608
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,080
that after Wang Zhi was placed under house arrest,

609
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,600
to prevent further accidents at the Western Depot,

610
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,440
this key is now

611
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:45,000
being carried by Consort Wan personally.

612
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:49,360
To prevent the deeds of the Western Depot

613
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:50,640
from being leaked, Consort Wan

614
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,440
immediately had the key fashioned into jewelry,

615
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:56,120
never letting it leave her side.

616
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:57,880
In that case,

617
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,360
if we want to get the key,

618
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,800
we must infiltrate the palace

619
00:32:03,560 --> 00:32:05,040
and steal it from Consort Wan.

620
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:11,400
That's nothing short of plucking hair from a tiger.

621
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,080
Plucking whiskers.

622
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:18,880
There's a rat.

623
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,600
They came for Blossom Pavilion.

624
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,640
I doubt it.

625
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:25,080
You are still working for Shang Hua.

626
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,000
Without his approval,

627
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,480
who would dare touch Blossom Pavilion?

628
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,280
They came for me.

629
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,680
They wanted to test me.

630
00:33:34,360 --> 00:33:37,080
It seems we must prepare for the worst for our operation.

631
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:41,800
We have already discovered at Blossom Pavilion that

632
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:43,520
Zhang Yi, Tang Xi, and the others

633
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,240
are indeed members of the Four Directions Organization.

634
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:47,200
And they are plotting,

635
00:33:47,560 --> 00:33:49,360
on the seventh day after Master Konghui's passing,

636
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,200
at the Prayer Lantern Festival,

637
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:52,280
to steal Consort Wan's nine-linked ring key.

638
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:59,000
Then should I

639
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:02,560
look forward to it?

640
00:34:11,240 --> 00:34:14,360
In the ancient capital of Nara,

641
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:19,640
the scent is strong today.

642
00:34:20,720 --> 00:34:23,960
The double cherry blossoms are in full bloom,

643
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:29,560
shining upon the nine-fold palace.

644
00:34:38,720 --> 00:34:40,080
For a moment today,

645
00:34:40,560 --> 00:34:42,200
I dared not look Yuan Ling in the eye.

646
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,040
Whether it was Zhang Yi,

647
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,880
or Zhang Yi's stance,

648
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,720
I simply could not

649
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:52,360
say anything against him.

650
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:57,640
I must go back.

651
00:34:58,320 --> 00:34:59,520
You should tell Zhang Yi and the others

652
00:34:59,520 --> 00:35:00,800
not to proceed with any plans.

653
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:02,200
All of their actions

654
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:03,360
are already being monitored by our Western Depot,

655
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:05,280
and even the Eastern Depot.

656
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,880
Their actions will only lead to death; they have no chance.

657
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,280
Isn't that betrayal?

658
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:20,680
I will make them pay the price

659
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,320
for their arrogance.

660
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:23,080
Yes.
